X Platform - Student Dashboard System Documentation

Project Overview

X Platform is an advanced e-learning platform designed initially for Jordanian Tawjihi students.

The platform currently supports:

Admin Dashboard
Teacher Dashboard
Student Dashboard
Subjects
Courses
Lessons
Protected video system
Course enrollment
Profile management
Role-based navigation

This stage introduced the Student Dashboard System and improved the public pages authentication behavior.

The main goal was to give students a clean dashboard where they can:

View their personal overview
View their enrolled courses
Enter their course lessons
Manage their profile information

The Student Dashboard was intentionally designed to be simple because students do not manage platform content.

Student Dashboard Purpose

The Student Dashboard was designed to provide students with a private learning area.

Students can:

View their account information
View their owned courses
Open course lessons
Edit their personal profile
Upload or update profile image

Students CANNOT:

Create courses
Edit courses
Delete courses
Create lessons
Upload videos
Manage users
Manage access codes
Manage purchases
Access teacher dashboard
Access admin dashboard

