Protected Route System

ProtectedRoute.tsx was improved.

Old behavior:

It depended mainly on:

localStorage.getItem("role")

Problem:

Sometimes the role existed inside the saved user object but not as a separate localStorage value.

Updated behavior:

ProtectedRoute now reads:

localStorage user object
role from parsed user
fallback role from localStorage

This makes route protection more reliable.

ProtectedRoute now supports:

student
teacher
admin

