Student Permissions System

A custom permission was created:

IsStudent

Purpose:

Allow only authenticated students to access student dashboard APIs.

Rule:

request.user.is_authenticated
AND
request.user.role == "student"

This prevents:

Teachers from accessing student APIs
Admins from using student-only APIs
Guests from accessing private student data

