Important Authentication Fix

Several old pages were still checking:

localStorage.getItem("access_token")

Problem:

The user was logged in through cookies, but the page thought the user was logged out because access_token did not exist in localStorage.

This caused wrong redirects to:

/login

The fix was to use:

localStorage.getItem("user")

instead of:

localStorage.getItem("access_token")

