CourseLessons Page Fix

File:

CourseLessons.tsx

Problem:

The lesson player redirected to Login even when the user was logged in.

Cause:

The page had:

const accessToken =
  localStorage.getItem("access_token") || localStorage.getItem("access");

Then:

if (!accessToken) navigate("/login")

This was incorrect because the current auth flow uses cookies.

Fix:

Removed accessToken check completely.
Removed useNavigate from CourseLessons.
Removed the redirect effect.

Now the page depends on backend API authorization.

Correct behavior:

If backend allows access:

Lessons load normally

If backend blocks access:

Show access error message

This is more secure because the backend is the real authority.

